# Unit 4: Lesson 8 - Rapid Research - Cybercrime

## Background

Learn about various types of cyber attacks and cyber crimes and do a small amount of research to learn more about one. The lesson caps off learning about encryption by taking a moment to look at the kinds of attacks and threats encryption (among other things) is intended to thwart.

## Vocabulary

* Phishing Scam
* DDoS Attack
* Virus / Anti-virus
* Firewall
* SSL/TLS (assoicated with HTTPS)

## Lesson

* Watch Video - Cybersecurity & Crime
* Read *How Not to Get Hacked*
* Reseach one type of cybercrime
* Share findings with another group
* Review cybersecurity terms


